==English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|slymy}}, {{m|enm|slimi}}, either derived from the noun {{inh|en|ang|slīm}} or an unattested {{l|ang|*slīmiġ}}, replacing {{inh|en|ang|slipig||slippy}}. Equivalent to {{af|en|slime|-y}}. Cognate with {{cog|nl|slijmig}}, {{m|nl|slijmerig|t=slimy}}, {{cog|de|schleimig|t=slimy; smarmy}}, {{cog|sv|slemmig|t=slimy}}.

